===============================================================================
            Plugin for connect CopterControl board to simulator.
===============================================================================


---------------------------------------
        Building
---------------------------------------

a) download and install:
    - Qt 4.8
    - MinGW 4.4
b) run:
    qmake
    mingw32-make


---------------------------------------
        Installing
---------------------------------------

a) Copy directory "CopterControl" from build location to simulator's "Plugin" folder.
b) Copy dep\*.dll from source tree to simulator's root folder.


---------------------------------------
        Configure plugin
---------------------------------------

CopterControl\cc_plugin.ini

    remote_host, remote_port - IP address and port of target
    local_host, local_port   - IP address and port of simulator



---------------------------------------
        Tools
---------------------------------------

udp_test utility can be used for test connection.

